<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Issue Created - Kirinyaga Adventist</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header img {
            width: 50%;
            max-width: 200px;
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        .title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 15px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .content {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #444;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding-top: 15px;
        }
        .social-icons img {
            width: 24px;
            margin: 5px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #007BFF;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        a {
            color: #007BFF;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header Image -->
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSdtQVCYDri-bQmVrsKUsdNFYFBfL9dVZG8Cw&s" alt="Issue Created">
        </div>

        <!-- Issue Notification Title -->
        <div class="title">
            Issue Reported Successfully
        </div>

        <!-- Issue Details -->
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= data.firstName %>,</p>
            <p>
                Thank you for reporting an issue to Kirinyaga Adventist. Our team will review it and get back to you as soon as possible.
            </p>

            <p><strong>Issue Title:</strong> <%= data.title %></p>

            <p>You can track the status of your issue by visiting your dashboard.</p>

            <p>If you need further assistance, please feel free to contact us.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>üôè Stay connected with us</p>

            <!-- Social Media Links -->
            <div class="social-icons">
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100083015178066" target="_blank">
                    <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/733/733547.png" alt="Facebook">
                </a>
                <a href="https://x.com/kyusdachurch?s=08" target="_blank">
                    <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/733/733579.png" alt="Twitter">
                </a>                
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@kyusdachurch9822" target="_blank">
                    <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/733/733646.png" alt="YouTube">
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
